Package dataStructure

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DWGraph_DS
    This class creates an directed weighted graph that holds the addition of nodes You can add new nodes, connect two nodes by ribs, delete nodes, delete ribs between two nodes, you can check if a rib exists, you can get a particular node, you can get the list of all the neighbors of a particular node and the list of nodes.
    EdgeData
    This class produces a edge object Each edge has a source node and target node and weight.
    NodeData
    This class allows you to create nodes with unique key and do various actions.
